    "department": "Sales",
    "description": "Whippy is leading the way in AI-powered business communication, transforming how companies engage with customers using intelligent AI Agents. From customer support to marketing to sales, businesses rely on Whippy’s Voice AI and Chat AI to eliminate manual workflows—responding to inquiries, nurturing leads, screening job applicants, and automating high-value interactions at scale. By combining AI-driven messaging with omni-channel automation, Whippy replaces outdated tools with a single, powerful platform that helps businesses work smarter, faster, and more efficiently.\n\n\n🚀 ABOUT THE ROLE\n\n - Whippy is seeking an all-star Sales Development Rep who thrives on high call volume, is resilient in the face of rejection, and excels in discovery, to join our dynamic team. OTE for this position $75,000. Hitting goals consistently will lead to promotion to Senior SDR.\n\n\n🌎 WHERE YOU'LL WORK\n\n - This is an in office position. Monday-Thursday we meet at 7am PST at our office in Culver City. Friday is remote from home.\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n⚡ WHAT YOU'LL DO\n\n - Own the sales cycle from qualifying the lead to setting up a demo for our AEs.\n\n - Conduct outbound sales across mediums such as cold calling, email outreach, Linkedin prospecting etc.\n\n - Manage a pipeline of active leads and utilize CRM (Hubspot)\n\n - Willing to refine sales messaging \u0026 strategies to achieve sales initiatives\n\n - Crush monthly Quotas\n\n\n🎯 WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR\n\n - 1+ years doing outbound sales utilizing sales enablement softwares\n\n - Proven experience doing a high number of daily cold calls (both office \u0026 mobile)\n\n - Created \u0026 conducted sales sequences including copy \u0026 testing\n\n - Extremely entrepreneurial given you would be an early sales hire\n\n - Strong desire to move towards a full cycle role and close deals\n\n - Want to work with a small team in an agile \u0026 scrappy startup environment\n\n - Do not need to be micro managed and can, when needed, figure things out on your own\n\n - Excellent written and verbal communication skills\n\n\n🙌 WHAT WE OFFER\n\n - Target OTE for this position is $75,000\n\n - Meaningful equity in a growing company (you are getting in on the ground floor)\n\n - Opportunity to take on significant responsibility and ownership in a highly disruptive product\n\n - Working hands-on with serial entrepreneurs who have created $100M+ valued companies",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
